.TH RODIN\-HEADLESS\-INSTALL 1 "2026-06-24" "rodin-headless @VERSION@" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
rodin\-headless\-install \- install Rodin and ProB for headless Event\-B builds
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B rodin\-headless\-install
.RI [ options ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B rodin\-headless\-install
downloads the Rodin IDE and the ProB CLI, points
.I rodin.ini
at the JVM on
.BR PATH ,
and installs the ProB/SMT/Atelier\ B Rodin plugins via the Eclipse p2
director. The result is a self\-contained native install that
.BR rodin\-headless (1)
detects automatically.
.PP
It never uses
.BR sudo :
required system packages (a JDK\ 21+, GTK3, Xvfb, zip/unzip) are reported by
.B \-\-check\-deps
with per\-distribution install hints rather than installed. The same script
is used inside the Docker image build, with
.BR "\-\-prefix /opt" .
.PP
Supported natively on Linux x86_64 and macOS (Intel and Apple\ Silicon; the
latter needs Rodin\ 3.10+). Re\-running is safe \(em completed phases are
skipped unless
.B \-\-force
is given.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.BI \-\-prefix " DIR"
Install prefix
.RI ( default " $RODIN_PREFIX" " or " ~/.local/share/rodin-headless ).
The layout is
.IR <prefix>/rodin " (the IDE) and " <prefix>/prob " (the ProB CLI)."
.TP
.BI \-\-only " rodin|prob"
Run a single install phase.
.TP
.B \-\-force
Reinstall even when a component is already present.
.TP
.BI \-\-rodin\-version " V"
.BR latest " (default), " latest\-rc ", or a specific version such as " 3.9 .
.TP
.BI \-\-rodin\-tarball " F"
Pin the exact tarball filename (skips detection; requires a specific
.BR \-\-rodin\-version ).
.TP
.BI \-\-prob\-version " V"
.BR latest " (default) or a specific version such as " 1.15.1 .
.TP
.B \-\-check\-deps
Report the status of system dependencies and exit.
.TP
.BR \-\-version ", " \-V
Print the program version and exit.
.TP
.BR \-h ", " \-\-help
Print usage and exit.
.SH ENVIRONMENT
.TP
.B RODIN_PREFIX
Default install prefix when
.B \-\-prefix
is not given.
.TP
.B RODIN_PLATFORM
Override platform detection
.RB ( linux\-x86_64 ", " macos\-x86_64 ", " macos\-aarch64 ).
.TP
.B RODIN_HEADLESS_LIBEXEC
Directory holding the shared library and version helper scripts.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Success, or
.B \-\-check\-deps
found no missing required dependency.
.TP
.B 1
An install error, a bad option, or a missing required dependency.
.SH FILES
.TP
.I <prefix>/.rodin-headless-versions
Manifest of the resolved Rodin and ProB versions.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR rodin\-headless (1)
.SH AUTHOR
Denis Efremov.
